<p:notes xmlns:a="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships" xmlns:p="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/presentationml/2006/main"><p:cSld><p:spTree><p:nvGrpSpPr><p:cNvPr id="1" name=""/><p:cNvGrpSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvGrpSpPr><p:grpSpPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="0" y="0"/><a:ext cx="0" cy="0"/><a:chOff x="0" y="0"/><a:chExt cx="0" cy="0"/></a:xfrm></p:grpSpPr><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="2" name="幻灯片图像占位符 1"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1" noRot="1" noChangeAspect="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="sldImg" idx="2"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr/></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="3" name="文本占位符 2"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="body" idx="3"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr/><p:txBody><a:bodyPr/><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>在对比学习中，编码模型是指用于将输入数据映射到低维表示（通常是向量空间）的模型，它可以是神经网络结构中的编码器部分。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>对比学习依赖于正例对和负例对，帮助模型学习对相似性和差异性进行区分。正例生成器和负例生成器负责产生这些对，让模型在训练过程中尽可能地将相似样本靠近，将不相似样本推远。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:rPr><a:t>正例生成器和负例生成器的设计是为了帮助模型更好地学习数据的特征和相似性，进而提高对比学习任务的效果，尤其对于学习有意义的表示和区分相似性非常重要。</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr><a:latin typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:ea typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:cs typeface="微软雅黑" panose="020B0503020204020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="-122"/><a:sym typeface="+mn-ea"/></a:endParaRPr></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="4" name="灯片编号占位符 3"/><p:cNvSpPr><a:spLocks noGrp="1"/></p:cNvSpPr><p:nvPr><p:ph type="sldNum" sz="quarter" idx="5"/></p:nvPr></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr/><p:txBody><a:bodyPr/><a:p><a:fld id="{1D0EAFC4-830A-47E7-8F93-2C2D15D9C629}" type="slidenum"><a:rPr lang="zh-CN" altLang="en-US" smtClean="0"/></a:fld><a:endParaRPr lang="zh-CN" altLang="en-US"/></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr></p:notes>